data.description: Welcome home to this one level home! The front room boasts a beautiful wood burning stove with white brick surround, sure to be a focal point for gatherings.  The kitchen features classic subway tile, granite counters, and sliding doors that lead to the covered patio, excellent for outdoor dining or lounging. Modern updates in the bathroom highlight a sleek and contemporary style.  The backyard is a blank canvas, waiting for your personal touch. It includes a large detached garage that could easily fit 3 cars. Power and heating are built in, making it the perfect, comfortable home work shop. This home is in a great location being close to the freeway and all the shopping and amenities that Clearfield and Layton has to offer.  All property information, boundaries and documents to be verified by buyer.
